The [[Thai language]] has many borrowed words from mainly [[Sanskrit]], [[Pali]] and some [[Prakrit]], [[Khmer language|Khmer]], [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]], [[Dutch language|Dutch]], certain [[Chinese dialects]] and more recently, [[Arabic]] (in particular many Islamic terms) and [[English language|English]] (in particular many scientific and technological terms). Some examples as follows:
