'''''Thunnus (Neothunnus)''''' is a [[subgenus]] of [[ray-finned]] [[bony fish]]es in the [[Thunnini]], or [[tuna]], [[tribe (biology)|tribe]].  More specifically, ''Neothunnus'' is a subgenus of the [[genus]] ''[[Thunnus]]'', also known as the "true tunas".  ''Neothunnus'' is sometimes referred to as the '''yellowfin group''', and comprises three species:

;subgenus ''Thunnus (Neothunnus)''
* ''[[Thunnus albacares|T. albacares]]'' <small>(Bonnaterre, 1788)</small> – [[yellowfin tuna]]
* ''[[Thunnus atlanticus|T. atlanticus]]'' <small>(Lesson, 1831)</small> – [[blackfin tuna]]
* ''[[Thunnus tonggol|T. tonggol]]'' <small>(Bleeker, 1851)</small> – [[longtail tuna]]

